      <title>阿斯利康 (AstraZeneca) 将以 10.5 亿美元收购 Amolyt Pharma，以增强罕见疾病产品组合</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-buy-amolyt-pharma-105-bln-boost-rare-diseases-portfolio-2024-03-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[制药商阿斯利康周四表示，将以 10.5 亿美元现金收购专注于罕见内分泌疾病的公司 Amolyt Pharma，以扩大其罕见疾病产品组合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-buy-amolyt-pharma-105-bln-boost-rare-diseases-portfolio-2024-03-14/</guid>
