      <title>Deliveroo 超出盈利预期，预计 2024 年现金流为正</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/deliveroo-beats-earnings-guidance-sees-positive-cash-flow-2024-2024-03-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国送餐公司Deliveroo公布的2023年核心盈利好于预期，为8500万英镑（1.09亿美元），并表示预计今年将取得进一步进展，预计将实现正现金流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/deliveroo-beats-earnings-guidance-sees-positive-cash-flow-2024-2024-03-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 07:11:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡大华银行计划到 2026 年将私人财富资产增加一倍</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/singaporean-bank-uob-aims-double-private-wealth-assets-by-2026-2024-03-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡银行大华银行（UOB）一位高管表示，该银行计划在未来几年将其管理的私人财富资产增加一倍，因为该银行押注更多财富流入新加坡和东南亚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/singaporean-bank-uob-aims-double-private-wealth-assets-by-2026-2024-03-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 07:09:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
